Kada klonirate projekat, napravite u htdocsu folder epos_zadatak i sve sa githuba prekopirajte tamo,
molim Vas da napravite u phpmyadminu bazu koja se zove epos_zadatak i udjete u SQL, nalepite sledeci kod i izvrsite,
takodje na desktopu napravite tekstualni fajl i nazovete ga po svom izboru,
prekopirate putanju do tog fajla i u kodu u index.php nadjete gde sam ja stavio moju putanju i umesto nje zalepite vasu,
nakon popunjavanja forme ako ste sve uradili kako treba trebalo bi da je korisnik dodat i u tekstualni fajl i u bazu

CREATE TABLE adminreg (
    admin_id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    first_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    last_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    password VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
);

When you clone the project, please create a folder named "epos_zadatak" in the 'htdocs' directory and then copy all the data from github into that folder,
Next, create a database named "epos_zadatak" in phpmyadmin and navigate to the SQL tab. Paste the following code there and execute it,
Additionally, create a txt file on your desktop, giving it any name you prefete. Copy the path of this txt file and replace my pathe in the index.php.
After you filled out the form, if you've followed all the steps correctly, the user will be added to both the txt file and the database
